This project is a TOOLKIT (operational scripts, documentation, CI patterns,
configuration templates) built ON TOP OF the upstream `engram` project by
Gentleman Programming. The `engram` binary, MCP server protocol, and SQLite
schema are NOT included nor modified by this project — they are consumed
unmodified as released by their authors.

For the upstream `engram` project license and copyright, see:
https://github.com/gentleman-programming/engram/blob/main/LICENSE

See also the ATTRIBUTION.md file in this repository for a full breakdown of
what this toolkit provides vs. what is upstream.
